{
  "stem": "1363.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they took us to another protected-- Swedish protected house quite far away, where we stayed and-- in a cellar.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There we were in the cellar.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I don't know, I think my papers by then, was not important.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But that was 6th of January.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the Russians were already in Budapest, on the borders of the city, so nobody worried about paper-- official papers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There weren't that many Germans around.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There were Nazis, Hungarian, the Nyilas.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And what we found out then, that in these last two weeks, a lot of these Swedish protected houses were gathered together, in-- the tenants or we thought there-- in-- living in ones, gathered together, took to the Danube, and were shot into the Danube by these Hungarian Nyilas.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Now, when I heard that, and I was still in one of the protected houses, we were scared that it happens to us, too.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But, we heard that not only were some of them shot in, but some of them were rescued by Jewish who were in uniform of the Nyilas.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Now, what they've done, they took all these Jews into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Because if the ghetto was protected, they were not allowed-- the Nyilas were not allowed to come into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was standing there and waiting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When am I going to see my grandma, and my auntie, and my-- my brother?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "None whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because what had happened in the meantime, they were one of the houses where the Jewish Nyilas took them into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they survived it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If they would have been with the Nyilas, they would have been in the Danube, dead, like all the others.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
